faq.question: What should I wear to the wedding?
faq.answer: Dress code is semi-formal. Think cocktail dresses or suit without a tie.

faq.question: Can I bring a guest?
faq.answer: Please refer to your invitation. If a guest is listed, they are welcome!

faq.question: Will there be parking available?
faq.answer: Yes, free parking will be available at the venue.
